## Do's and Don'ts Compliance (Section 18)

| Rule | Status |
|---|---|
| Use structured JSON prompts | âś… All prompts return strict JSON |
| Validate all user inputs | âś… `validate_job_description()` + `validate_answer()` |
| Use retry logic for invalid responses | âś… `extract_json_with_retry()` â€” 3 retries |
| Store configuration in .env | âś… `python-dotenv` used everywhere |
| Use modular architecture | âś… 5 separate modules |
| Show loading spinners | âś… `st.spinner()` on all LLM calls |
| Use session state properly | âś… `st.session_state` + autosave |
| Do NOT hardcode API keys | âś… All via `.env` |
| Do NOT trust raw LLM responses | âś… JSON extraction + validation layer |
| Do NOT use global variables | âś… All state via `InterviewSession` |
| Do NOT expose Python tracebacks | âś… All errors caught and shown as `st.error()` |
| Do NOT skip edge-case testing | âś… Empty input, short input, LLM failure, injection all tested |

